::Repression Status

{repression_level}
(..2.999): State violence is minimal. The regime is cautious.
(2.999..7.999): There are occasional crackdowns. Most protests are tolerated.
(7.999..20.999): Repression is escalating. Demonstrators face serious risk.
(20.999..35.999): The streets are dangerous. Dissidents are routinely jailed or worse.
(35.999..): The regime is in full terror mode. Open opposition is nearly suicidal.
